### REST API - Create Order
POST http://localhost:8000/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "a",
  "price": 100.50,
  "tax": 10.00
}

###

### REST API - List Orders
GET http://localhost:8000/order

###

### GraphQL - Create Order
POST http://localhost:8080/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { createOrder(input: { id: \"b\", price: 200.00, tax: 20.00 }) { id price tax finalPrice } }"
}

###

### GraphQL - List Orders
POST http://localhost:8080/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ orders { id price tax finalPrice } }"
}

###

### gRPC - Interactive Mode
evans -r repl -p 50051

###

### gRPC - CLI Create Order
echo '{"id":"c","price":300,"tax":30}' | evans --host localhost --port 50051 -r cli call pb.OrderService.CreateOrder

###

### gRPC - CLI List Orders
echo '{}' | evans --host localhost --port 50051 -r cli call pb.OrderService.ListOrders

###
